The target screen receives the params via its `route` prop:

```jsx
function DetailsScreen({ route }) {
  const { itemId, otherParam } = route.params;

  return (
    <View>
      <Text>Item ID: {itemId}</Text>
      <Text>Other: {otherParam}</Text>
    </View>
  );
}
```

If no params are passed, `route.params` is `undefined`. You can provide default values:

```jsx
const { itemId = 0 } = route.params ?? {};
```
